message.content: cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MED, cs.NEURON - The paper deals with segmentation of small organs in whole-body MRI scans using deep learning techniques. This falls under the domain of computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). Additionally, the paper deals with medical imaging (cs.MED) and uses auto-context and spatial atlas priors, which are commonly used in neuroimaging (cs.NEURON).
